{"date":"2004-10-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/8f/5f/24329_vtKD6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/8f/5f/24329_vtKD6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/8f/5f/24329_vtKD6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/8f/5f/24329_vtKD6.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/8f/5f/24329_vtKD6.jpg"},"summary":"　　关东大沙漠是一片可怕的死亡之地，数百年前，繁荣的文明毁于一旦，只留下沙海中默默矗立的高楼废墟，如墓碑般渲染着浓重的死亡气息。这里白天温度超过50摄氏度，到了夜晚又骤降到零下，环境极其恶劣。即使在这种地狱般的世界里，仍然活动着顽强的人类。\r\n　　关东沙漠通用的法则是金钱和力量，每个人都为自己的生存而战，各种丑恶的现象显得如此正常。其中有一个被称作“砂和尚”的少年，他原名水野灌太，对沙漠了如指掌的他在这里乾着代理人的工作，为了生存以及完成任务不择手段，因此被称作“沙漠的妖怪”。和他在一起的助手则是被称作“小沙”的女孩小泉太湖。在充满危险的大沙漠里，一个残酷的生存故事即将开始…… ","name":"砂ぼうず","name_cn":"砂和尚","tags":[{"name":"GONZO","count":47,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2004","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":34,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":29,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫画改","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"漫改","count":15,"total_cont":0},{"name":"砂和尚","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"热血","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"斋藤千和","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神結局","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2004年10月","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"稻垣隆行","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"卖肉","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"福利","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"福利番","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"肉番","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"稲垣隆行","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"战斗","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"山口宏","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2004秋","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SF","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2000s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"铃木千寻","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神作","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"鈴木千尋","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"砂和尚"},{"key":"